    return thaw_json_value(self.source_state_inputs)
```

**Frontend API Serialization:** `/home/kelvin/bayes-market/frontend/src/lib/api/client.ts`
```typescript
// All POST/PUT/PATCH requests use JSON.stringify on payload
body: JSON.stringify(payload)

